reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very sturdy and stable
reviews.reviewText: Surprisingly easy to put together. Very sturdy and structurally strong and stable. I have it holding a microwave and a separate convection oven, and a large Excalibir dehydrator on top. The shelves are adjustable in height, so you can customize the rack for what you are putting on it. I like that it has a side rack for holding cutting boards, plus a towel rack, plus two sizes (8 each!) of hooks for holding additional objects. It is so convenient to have things handy. I added a magnetic paper towel rack to the side also.I definitely recommend this rack for any kitchen! It certainly cleared up a lot of counter space and looks great, while making appliances more convenient to use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Seems sturdy and good for my needs
reviews.reviewText: I struggled a little with the assembly. It felt like I needed an extra pair of hands, but I finally got it together.There was a piece missing in one of the legs where you screw in the foot. I did find something I had in my variety of screws and things that I got to work. I didn't contact the seller about it because I did get the product together OK. It seems rather sturdy and all in all, I believe this will work well for my purposes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I needed
reviews.reviewText: Living in an RV, counterspace is at a premium, and the designer’s choice to put the microwave over the stove is a hazard for hubby and I having to get on a ladder to get items in and out of it. Yesterday I had an idea that this might work, so I ordered it. Stand arrived this morning, went together in less than 30 minutes and it fits perfectly where I needed it to. My unit is a microwave/convection oven so it’s larger than most so it was very helpful to have the adjusting width. Now we can keep our toaster oven out also, instead of having to keep it in a cupboard. Can’t wait to start baking my pumpkin pies and be able to get them into the oven without spillage.Only issue is that when I ordered the unit, I got notification that seller was no longer stocking this item and to choose another seller. I did (costlier) and imagine my surprise this morning when I got notice that the original one I wanted (this unit) would be delivered within an hour. The second one wouldn’t be here until Wednesday. Luckily, I wa able to cancel the order as it hadn’t yet shipped.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: Easy to assemble and to look at. It does the intended job.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars worth the money
reviews.reviewText: I think it would have helped if it had a few cross bars on the back side to make it more sturdy but for $30 its hard to argue about. The biggest complaint was that I had to straighten parts of it (as best as I could) from the damage done to it during shipping. Two of the end panels were significantly bowed in and one of the screws had no threads. Luckily it came with an extra screw. Also the small hooks that attach on the end may as well be trashed when you open the box. They are plastic and wont last long. Go get something better at you're local hardware store.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I loved that this was so easy to assemble. I really didn't even need someone to help. I have an older, larger microwave but it sits underneath easily.I especially liked the hooks on the sides, as they hold coffee cups nicely. This was a great solution for an awkward space in my kitchen. Now it's much more functional for such a little bit of money, time and effort.Mine is very sturdy, even though I have it expanded almost to the fullest extension point.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Returned this as it isn't sturdy when extended the metal is thin and there is no brace to stop it from separating! The wider you make it the weaker it gets.
I love my new stand! It cleaned up my coffee area perfectly! No more clutter all over the place. Easy to put together and adjust width to what you need. Highly recommend this!

reviews.reviewTitle: Had to return and order a second one due to missing parts
reviews.reviewText: Edited to add:The second shelf that arrived (to replace the one I sent back that was missing parts) arrived in a box that was partially open. However, the shelf unit inside was not damaged at all and it had all the necessary parts (and a few extra hooks and screws). It was quick and easy to assemble and will make the perfect shelf for my Cricut machines so that I can run more than one at the same time. I am glad that I didn't give up on the product based on my initial experience._______________________________The item arrived in a sealed box which had no damage or evidence of having been opened previously. However, there were pieces missing, specifically all the screws, that are essential to being able to assemble the shelves. It was also missing all of the levelling feet, the wrench and all of the hooks.Initially I hunted for screws locally that I would be able to use to assemble the product, but quickly realized that spending additional money on something that I had already paid a good price for was ridiculous. Therefore, I have opted to return the product and reorder it. Hopefully when the new one arrives it will have all the necessary pieces, otherwise it too will end up being returned.

Both of the shelves were bent and warped when we opened this product. Must have happened before shipping as the box it came in was not damaged. Disappointing for something that is supposed to be sturdy

It seemed like a great shelf, but without the screws and things to put it together I didn't get a chance to use it. The storefront was in contact in a reasonable time, and amazon refunded the payment without issue. Therefore, I have reordered.
